title: WEDNESDAY 3/3 - JJ Watt in the Valle of the Sun
itunes:title: WEDNESDAY 3/3 - JJ Watt in the Valle of the Sun
description:
JJ Watt signing a two-year deal to join the Cardinals. He talked about his decision to head to Arizona (0:08). The Bears with a decision to make on Allen Robinson's (1:45) future in Chicago, as the Packers need to do the same with Aaron Jones (2:28). More news out of the NFC North as tight end Kyle Rudolph's time with the Vikings has come to an end (3:33)
